        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego frater <persName key="d1e26422" xml:id="d1e159488">Radulphus dictus abbas
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283145" xml:id="d1e159490" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Longuay (1102 -)">Longi Vadi</orgName>
                    </persName> et frater <persName key="d1e26428" xml:id="d1e159493">Robertus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324328" xml:id="d1e159495" corresp="Aignay-le-Duc (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Ainnaio</placeName>
                        Ungiaci canonicus</persName> volumus notum fieri presentibus et futuris quod
                    sicut nobis a <persName key="d1e26434" xml:id="d1e159499">domino
                        Eduensi</persName> et <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324677" xml:id="d1e159502" corresp="Gaucher, abbé de Flavigny (1173-1185)">
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e159503" corresp="abbaye Saint-Pierre et Saint-Prix de Flavigny">Flaviniaci</orgName>
                    </persName> et <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281589" xml:id="d1e159506" corresp="abbaye d'Hautecombe (1121 -)">
                        <persName key="d1e26441" xml:id="d1e159507">Alte Cumbe</persName>
                    </orgName> abbatibus commissum fuit <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325210" xml:id="d1e159511" corresp="silvam de Leurce">silvam de <foreign>Leurce</foreign>
                    </placeName> partiti sumus, reddentes <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e159516" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneto</orgName> et <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e159519" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)">Ungiaco</orgName> partem suam, laude et assensu utriusque
                    capituli sicut mete lapidee ibidem posite designant. Hac scilicet conditione
                    quod neutra pars in parte alterius deinceps aliquid adquirere poterit nec
                    habere. Et quia fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e159522" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)">Ungiacenses</orgName> edificia sua in territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325286" xml:id="d1e159525" corresp="Frimasii">Frimasii</placeName> mutaverunt ubi
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e159528" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName>
                    medietatem habebant secundum quantitatem loci ubi priora edificia fuerant in
                    illo loco ubi postea edificaverunt cum orto illo et veridario que ibi prius
                    habuerant, tantumdem spacii sicut nobis commissum fuerat eis in pace
                    concessimus. Quod vero superfuit in clausura grangie per medium divisimus
                    medietatem <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e159532" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)">Ungiacensibus</orgName> assignantes et pro altera medietate utriusque
                    partis assensu commutationem congruam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e159535" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensibus</orgName> reddentes. Ad testimonium hujus
                    rei ego <persName key="d1e26447" xml:id="d1e159538">Radulphus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283145" xml:id="d1e159540" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Longuay (1102 -)">Longi Vadi</orgName>
                    </persName> scripto huic sigillum meum apposui et ego <persName key="d1e26453" xml:id="d1e159543">Arverius abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e159545" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)">Ungiaci</orgName>
                    </persName> ut hec rata permaneant sigilli nostri appositione confirmo. Hinc
                    testes sunt <persName key="d1e26459" xml:id="d1e159548">Bartholomeus prior
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" xml:id="d1e159550" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)">Ungiaci</orgName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e26465" xml:id="d1e159553">Hugo cantor <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283145" xml:id="d1e159555" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Longuay (1102 -)">Longi Vadi</orgName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e26471" xml:id="d1e159559">Galterius</persName> et
                        <persName key="d1e26478" xml:id="d1e159562">Bernardus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e159564" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        monachi</persName>.</p>
            </body>
